Thank you for watching.
This is my loopstation wildcard for Grand Beatbox Battle 2025 World League.
I was inspired by the songs in movies such as The Greatest Showman to create this track. In creating this track, I aimed to make it simple and easy to understand, moving, and to make the most of the voice.
